{"tid":392342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傅振中：支持余若蓮","createTime":"2017-09-08T12:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T13:30:33.000Z","uid":6604,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e26e55d04e7044ea1bbf0a98351697e7b6acfcb","tid":392342,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170908/57185109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170908%2F57185109&d=Bvvsqcn33n%2BdvmuLYF6VpY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6df7d70f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170908%2F57185109&h=694878ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170908/57185109</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保衛香港運動約40名中年人士穿著白衣戴藍帽，手執國旗、區旗、示威牌及橫額到教大集會，促請教大徹查蔡若蓮事件，並交請願信予教大代表，多次大叫喊「我要教育學院（大學），不要禽獸學院」，稱要維護香港教育大學聲譽，嚴懲侮辱蔡若者涉事者。保衛香港運動主席傅振中開口首句講錯「<span style=\"color: red;\">支持余若蓮</span>」，又指不會如昨日珍惜群組與學生發生紛爭，不想破壞學校寧靜，所以不會到民主牆，叫口號及遞交請願信後便立即離開教大。<br />\n<br />\n保衛香港運動指教大培育的學生將來大多成為老師，不應説出無人性的言論，應指擔心如涉事者真的是學生，會在教育界遺害學子，於涉事者是校外人士，校方必定要加強保安。團體約逗留半小時後離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3032c8489b671fb21977b9f045def67b5dfbe49","tid":392342,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582a1dde0c55eb5980d1b850afc98ffb98d38c08","tid":392342,"uid":49532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:22:15.000Z","msg":"支持余慕蓮"},{"pid":"6adce19ae172f3900b06e82f3bac0d84044a28aa","tid":392342,"uid":53164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"定係想支持余若薇"},{"pid":"b1550630d685